Navigating the world as a sensitive explorer. It can feel very intense at times, but as we learn to honour our slowness and when we consider our sensitivity as a strength and guide, things become a little bit easier. To be sensitive is to be attuned to deep listening, deep feeling. A reminder to be kind to yourself as you navigate this world. 

